data.content: (kỹ thuật) nguyên cảo; nguyên đồ; đồ trang sức; đồ nghệ thuật

noun
plural -works
a painting, sculpture, photograph, etc., that is created to be beautiful or to express an important idea or feeling :an artistic work [noncount]
A local painter was selling her artwork on the street.
The walls of the restaurant are decorated in original artwork.
Some of the children's artwork was hanging on the refrigerator. [count]
The museum recently recovered two stolen artworks.
contemporary artworks
[noncount] :drawings, photographs, etc., that are included in books, magazines, and other printed materials
